item.title: CVE-2023-6946|2024-01-29T14:44:22.240Z -- unknown -- autotitle%20for%20wordpress
item.description: The Autotitle for WordPress plugin through 1.0.3 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change them via a CSRF attack.
